Titolo: Freedom Fighters (video game)

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Freedom Fighters is a 2003 third-person shooter video game for the PlayStation 2, GameCube, Xbox and Microsoft Windows. It was developed by IO Interactive and published by Electronic Arts.The game is set in an alternate history where the Soviet Union has invaded and occupied New York City. The player takes the role of Christopher Stone, a plumber turned resistance movement leader, fighting against the invaders.The game was re-released digitally on September 21, 2020, by IO Interactive for PC on Steam, GOG, and Epic Games Store. Included in the purchase of the re-release is the full "Official Freedom Fighters soundtrack" together with 2 bonus tracks that were never included in the game.

Genere: Third-person shooter

Valutazione: N/A
